{"tid":2333372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：我為甚麼一直支持特朗普？","createTime":"2020-12-20T10:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T03:11:09.000Z","uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9e76db693729bde14f4f5305e27bb94abab15e80","tid":2333372,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:39:29.000Z","msg":"於本土而言，特朗普上台，中美鬧翻，為香港經濟和政治帶來災難。<br />\n他強迫中國貨物加稅和強迫中國輸入美國農產品，號令工業遷出中國，搬去越南和印度，為中國的工人階級和廣大農民帶來災難，足以令中國哀鴻遍野。然則，於天下而言，特朗普糾正左膠邪道，煞停社會主義的歪風邪氣，解救美國工農階級，也最終解救香港及中國。<br />\n我一直支持特朗普，不是出自本土或中國私心，而是出自天下公心。這就是儒家政治的情懷，正如孔子讚賞齊國的宰相管仲，雖然管仲令齊國強大之後經常欺負孔子的魯國（齊國一向欺負魯國），但孔子認為，沒有管仲輔助齊國中興，諸夏的天下都會蠻夷化。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vbgr2f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVbgr2f3.jpg&h=5661cbe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-20-2020/68930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-20-2020%2F68930&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=50a5e857\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-20-2020/68930</a>"},{"pid":"6d8b7616c625f9441adb760c33eaf46d21e5140d","tid":2333372,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T10:49:48.000Z","msg":"金毛仔"},{"pid":"2ee1fd8d2fa5f468e8a77a32b41ce40a1fcaaa04","tid":2333372,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"其實陳雲🌭,  右膠 ,反抗疫, 愛侵力<br />\n<br />\n大家似而不同,經常係cctoy彈四重奏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n間中有pr狗伴奏🎼🔊"},{"pid":"d674ebf76c774b6deb1f0f373b2aee14a100bbfe","tid":2333372,"uid":363413,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"佢之前唔係話特朗普針對佢，之後要黃天擊殺特朗普咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26dd3153425ffaeb19345a4d3064c5fe20719b28","t